{"tid":1676671,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now Sports-體育】李城粉絲向已故班主致敬 羅渣士動容","createTime":"2019-10-26T15:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T18:17:16.000Z","uid":202340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5ec33ec7f441d16e4e55efa36c97c3a220f2a050","tid":1676671,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】已故李斯特城班主維猜逝世1周年，領隊羅渣士對球迷的行為動容不已。<br />\n1年前，維猜在直升機事故中喪生，數千李斯特城球迷於上場對般尼時向前班主作出致敬。李城周五對修得手，把比分拉近至122:123，不過當比賽最後一刻，他跳射未能命中，最終球隊以126:127飲恨。 籃網是役5名正選中有4人得分達雙位數，除K.艾榮得全場最高的50分外，利維治及派斯分別得20分及15分。木狼的唐斯與域堅斯分別得36分及21分。 同日戰況亦緊湊的首推黃蜂迎擊公牛，結果主隊憑華盛頓攻入27分，以126:125力克公牛。至於杜蒙特攻入32分及摘下23個籃板，協助119:110打敗主場的溜馬。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E6%9D%8E%E5%9F%8E%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%90%91%E5%B7%B2%E6%95%85%E7%8F%AD%E4%B8%BB%E8%87%B4%E6%95%AC-%E7%BE%85%E6%B8%A3%E5%A3%AB%E5%8B%95%E5%AE%B9-011905151--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2595%2585%25E7%258F%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%2595%25AC-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%25AE%25B9-011905151--spt.html&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=07cea380\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E6%9D%8E%E5%9F%8E%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E5%90%91%E5%B7%B2%E6%95%85%E7%8F%AD%E4%B8%BB%E8%87%B4%E6%95%AC-%E7%BE%85%E6%B8%A3%E5%A3%AB%E5%8B%95%E5%AE%B9-011905151--spt.html</a><br />\n--------<br />\n我原文copy , now 食錯藥"},{"pid":"f46f4f4cc4aff2ce9b9b60a4013cde9d1b6ff801","tid":1676671,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803ae52114c03a36b5ff0a917a2bd1911a5162f5","tid":1676671,"uid